targets.rawSql:
WITH deltas AS (
  SELECT
    bucket,
    queryid,
    calls - LAG(calls) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY bucket) AS delta_calls,
    total_time - LAG(total_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY bucket) AS delta_total_time,
    blk_read_time - LAG(blk_read_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY bucket) AS delta_blk_read_time,
    blk_write_time - LAG(blk_write_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY bucket) AS delta_blk_write_time
  FROM pganalyze.stat_statements_cagg
  WHERE $__timeFilter(bucket)
),
expanded AS (
  SELECT
    bucket,
    delta_calls,
    (delta_total_time / NULLIF(delta_calls, 0)::double precision) AS per_call_latency,
    (delta_blk_read_time + delta_blk_write_time) / NULLIF(delta_calls, 0)::double precision AS per_call_io_time
  FROM deltas
  WHERE delta_calls > 0 AND delta_total_time >= 0
),
aggregated AS (
  SELECT
    bucket,
    percentile_agg(per_call_latency) AS latency_percentiles,
    avg(per_call_io_time) AS avg_io
  FROM expanded
  GROUP BY bucket
)
SELECT
  bucket,
  approx_percentile(0.5, latency_percentiles) AS "Median time",
  approx_percentile(0.95, latency_percentiles) AS "P95 time",
  avg_io AS "Avg I/O time"
FROM aggregated
ORDER BY bucket;

WITH deltas AS (
  SELECT
    queryid::text,
    query,
    calls - LAG(calls) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY bucket) AS delta_calls,
    total_time - LAG(total_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY bucket) AS delta_total_time,
    blk_read_time - LAG(blk_read_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY bucket) AS delta_blk_read_time,
    blk_write_time - LAG(blk_write_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY bucket) AS delta_blk_write_time
  FROM pganalyze.stat_statements_cagg
  WHERE $__timeFilter(bucket)
),
filtered AS (
  SELECT *
  FROM deltas
  WHERE delta_calls > 0 AND delta_total_time > 0
),
totals AS (
  SELECT
    SUM(delta_total_time) AS total_runtime,
    SUM(delta_blk_read_time + delta_blk_write_time) AS total_io
  FROM filtered
)
SELECT
  queryid,
  MAX(query) AS "Query",
  SUM(delta_total_time) / NULLIF(SUM(delta_calls), 0) AS "Avg time",
  SUM(delta_calls)::numeric / COUNT(*) AS "Calls/min",
  SUM(delta_blk_read_time + delta_blk_write_time) * 100.0 / NULLIF(t.total_io, 0) AS "% of all I/O",
  SUM(delta_total_time) * 100.0 / NULLIF(t.total_runtime, 0) AS "% of all runtime"
FROM filtered
JOIN totals t ON true
GROUP BY queryid, t.total_io, t.total_runtime
ORDER BY "% of all runtime" DESC
LIMIT 100;

WITH pre_aggregated AS (
  SELECT
    time_bucket(INTERVAL '$__interval', collected_at) AS bucket,
    collected_at,
    SUM(calls) AS calls,
    SUM(total_time) AS total_time,
    SUM(blk_read_time) AS blk_read_time,
    SUM(blk_write_time) AS blk_write_time
  FROM pganalyze.stat_statements
  WHERE queryid = $queryid AND $__timeFilter(collected_at)
  GROUP BY collected_at
),
deltas AS (
  SELECT
    time_bucket(INTERVAL '$__interval', collected_at) AS bucket,
    calls - LAG(calls) OVER (ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_calls,
    total_time - LAG(total_time) OVER (ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_total_time,
    blk_read_time - LAG(blk_read_time) OVER (ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_read_time,
    blk_write_time - LAG(blk_write_time) OVER (ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_write_time
  FROM pre_aggregated
),
filtered AS (
  SELECT *
  FROM deltas
  WHERE delta_calls > 0 AND delta_total_time >= 0
)
SELECT
  bucket AS time,
  SUM(delta_total_time) / NULLIF(SUM(delta_calls), 0) AS "Avg total time",
  SUM(delta_blk_read_time + delta_blk_write_time) AS "Avg I/O time",
  SUM(delta_calls) AS "Calls"
FROM filtered
GROUP BY bucket
ORDER BY bucket;

matcher.options: Bytes read from disk per call

targets.rawSql:
WITH deltas AS (
  SELECT
    time_bucket(INTERVAL '$__interval', collected_at) AS bucket,
    calls - LAG(calls) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_calls,
    total_time - LAG(total_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_total_time,
    blk_read_time - LAG(blk_read_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_read_time,
    blk_write_time - LAG(blk_write_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_write_time,
    shared_blks_hit - LAG(shared_blks_hit) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_shared_blks_hit,
    shared_blks_read - LAG(shared_blks_read) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_shared_blks_read
  FROM pganalyze.stat_statements
  WHERE queryid = $queryid AND $__timeFilter(collected_at)
),
filtered AS (
  SELECT *
  FROM deltas
  WHERE delta_calls > 0 AND delta_total_time >= 0
)
SELECT
  bucket AS time,
  
  -- Calculate % from buffer cache (cache hits)
  CASE WHEN SUM(delta_shared_blks_hit + delta_shared_blks_read) > 0
       THEN 100.0 * SUM(delta_shared_blks_hit)::float / SUM(delta_shared_blks_hit + delta_shared_blks_read)
       ELSE NULL
  END AS "Percent from buffer cache",

  -- % from disk (reads)
  CASE WHEN SUM(delta_shared_blks_hit + delta_shared_blks_read) > 0
       THEN 100.0 * SUM(delta_shared_blks_read)::float / SUM(delta_shared_blks_hit + delta_shared_blks_read)
       ELSE NULL
  END AS "Percent from disk",

  -- Bytes read from disk per call (blocks * 8KB)
  CASE WHEN SUM(delta_calls) > 0
       THEN (SUM(delta_shared_blks_read) * 8192)::float / SUM(delta_calls)
       ELSE NULL
  END AS "Bytes read from disk per call"

FROM filtered
GROUP BY bucket
ORDER BY bucket;

SELECT time AS "Executed at",
total_cost AS "Est. cost",
duration AS "Runtime",
io_read_time AS "I/O read time",
io_read_time / duration * 100.0 AS "I/O read time %",
bytes_read AS "Read from disk",
queryid::text,
plan
FROM pganalyze.stat_explains
WHERE queryid = $queryid 
ORDER BY time DESC

{
  "Query Text": "WITH pre_aggregated AS (\n  SELECT\n    collected_at,\n    queryid::text,\n    MAX(query) AS query,\n    SUM(calls) AS calls,\n    SUM(total_time) AS total_time,\n    SUM(blk_read_time) AS blk_read_time,\n    SUM(blk_write_time) AS blk_write_time\n  FROM pganalyze.stat_statements\n  WHERE collected_at BETWEEN '2025-08-04T09:48:30.909Z' AND '2025-08-11T09:48:30.909Z'\n  GROUP BY collected_at, queryid\n),\ndeltas AS (\n  SELECT\n    queryid,\n    query,\n    calls - LAG(calls) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_calls,\n    total_time - LAG(total_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_total_time,\n    blk_read_time - LAG(blk_read_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_read_time,\n    blk_write_time - LAG(blk_write_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_write_time\n  FROM pre_aggregated\n),\nfiltered AS (\n  SELECT *\n  FROM deltas\n  WHERE delta_calls > 0 AND delta_total_time > 0\n),\ntotals AS (\n  SELECT\n    SUM(delta_total_time) AS total_runtime,\n    SUM(delta_blk_read_time   delta_blk_write_time) AS total_io\n  FROM filtered\n)\nSELECT\n  queryid,\n  MAX(query) AS \"Query\",\n  SUM(delta_total_time) / NULLIF(SUM(delta_calls), 0) AS \"Avg time\",\n  SUM(delta_calls)::numeric / COUNT(*) AS \"Calls/min\",\n  SUM(delta_blk_read_time   delta_blk_write_time) * 100.0 / NULLIF(t.total_io, 0) AS \"% of all I/O\",\n  SUM(delta_total_time) * 100.0 / NULLIF(t.total_runtime, 0) AS \"% of all runtime\"\nFROM filtered\nJOIN totals t ON true\nGROUP BY queryid, t.total_io, t.total_runtime\nORDER BY \"% of all runtime\" DESC\nLIMIT 100;\n",

{
  "Query Text": "WITH pre_aggregated AS (\n  SELECT\n    collected_at,\n    queryid::text,\n    MAX(query) AS query,\n    SUM(calls) AS calls,\n    SUM(total_time) AS total_time,\n    SUM(blk_read_time) AS blk_read_time,\n    SUM(blk_write_time) AS blk_write_time\n  FROM pganalyze.stat_statements\n  WHERE collected_at BETWEEN '2025-08-04T09:48:30.909Z' AND '2025-08-11T09:48:30.909Z'\n  GROUP BY collected_at, queryid\n),\ndeltas AS (\n  SELECT\n    queryid,\n    query,\n    calls - LAG(calls) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_calls,\n    total_time - LAG(total_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_total_time,\n    blk_read_time - LAG(blk_read_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_read_time,\n    blk_write_time - LAG(blk_write_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_write_time\n  FROM pre_aggregated\n),\nfiltered AS (\n  SELECT *\n  FROM deltas\n  WHERE delta_calls > 0 AND delta_total_time > 0\n),\ntotals AS (\n  SELECT\n    SUM(delta_total_time) AS total_runtime,\n    SUM(delta_blk_read_time   delta_blk_write_time) AS total_io\n  FROM filtered\n)\nSELECT\n  queryid,\n  MAX(query) AS \"Query\",\n  SUM(delta_total_time) / NULLIF(SUM(delta_calls), 0) AS \"Avg time\",\n  SUM(delta_calls)::numeric / COUNT(*) AS \"Calls/min\",\n  SUM(delta_blk_read_time   delta_blk_write_time) * 100.0 / NULLIF(t.total_io, 0) AS \"% of all I/O\",\n  SUM(delta_total_time) * 100.0 / NULLIF(t.total_runtime, 0) AS \"% of all runtime\"\nFROM filtered\nJOIN totals t ON true\nGROUP BY queryid, t.total_io, t.total_runtime\nORDER BY \"% of all runtime\" DESC\nLIMIT 100;\n",

{
  "Query Text": "WITH pre_aggregated AS (\n  SELECT\n    collected_at,\n    queryid::text,\n    MAX(query) AS query,\n    SUM(calls) AS calls,\n    SUM(total_time) AS total_time,\n    SUM(blk_read_time) AS blk_read_time,\n    SUM(blk_write_time) AS blk_write_time\n  FROM pganalyze.stat_statements\n  WHERE collected_at BETWEEN '2025-08-04T09:48:30.909Z' AND '2025-08-11T09:48:30.909Z'\n  GROUP BY collected_at, queryid\n),\ndeltas AS (\n  SELECT\n    queryid,\n    query,\n    calls - LAG(calls) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_calls,\n    total_time - LAG(total_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_total_time,\n    blk_read_time - LAG(blk_read_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_read_time,\n    blk_write_time - LAG(blk_write_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_write_time\n  FROM pre_aggregated\n),\nfiltered AS (\n  SELECT *\n  FROM deltas\n  WHERE delta_calls > 0 AND delta_total_time > 0\n),\ntotals AS (\n  SELECT\n    SUM(delta_total_time) AS total_runtime,\n    SUM(delta_blk_read_time   delta_blk_write_time) AS total_io\n  FROM filtered\n)\nSELECT\n  queryid,\n  MAX(query) AS \"Query\",\n  SUM(delta_total_time) / NULLIF(SUM(delta_calls), 0) AS \"Avg time\",\n  SUM(delta_calls)::numeric / COUNT(*) AS \"Calls/min\",\n  SUM(delta_blk_read_time   delta_blk_write_time) * 100.0 / NULLIF(t.total_io, 0) AS \"% of all I/O\",\n  SUM(delta_total_time) * 100.0 / NULLIF(t.total_runtime, 0) AS \"% of all runtime\"\nFROM filtered\nJOIN totals t ON true\nGROUP BY queryid, t.total_io, t.total_runtime\nORDER BY \"% of all runtime\" DESC\nLIMIT 100;\n",

list.query:
{
  "Query Text": "WITH pre_aggregated AS (\n  SELECT\n    collected_at,\n    queryid::text,\n    MAX(query) AS query,\n    SUM(calls) AS calls,\n    SUM(total_time) AS total_time,\n    SUM(blk_read_time) AS blk_read_time,\n    SUM(blk_write_time) AS blk_write_time\n  FROM pganalyze.stat_statements\n  WHERE collected_at BETWEEN '2025-08-04T09:48:30.909Z' AND '2025-08-11T09:48:30.909Z'\n  GROUP BY collected_at, queryid\n),\ndeltas AS (\n  SELECT\n    queryid,\n    query,\n    calls - LAG(calls) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_calls,\n    total_time - LAG(total_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_total_time,\n    blk_read_time - LAG(blk_read_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_read_time,\n    blk_write_time - LAG(blk_write_time) OVER (PARTITION BY queryid ORDER BY collected_at) AS delta_blk_write_time\n  FROM pre_aggregated\n),\nfiltered AS (\n  SELECT *\n  FROM deltas\n  WHERE delta_calls > 0 AND delta_total_time > 0\n),\ntotals AS (\n  SELECT\n    SUM(delta_total_time) AS total_runtime,\n    SUM(delta_blk_read_time   delta_blk_write_time) AS total_io\n  FROM filtered\n)\nSELECT\n  queryid,\n  MAX(query) AS \"Query\",\n  SUM(delta_total_time) / NULLIF(SUM(delta_calls), 0) AS \"Avg time\",\n  SUM(delta_calls)::numeric / COUNT(*) AS \"Calls/min\",\n  SUM(delta_blk_read_time   delta_blk_write_time) * 100.0 / NULLIF(t.total_io, 0) AS \"% of all I/O\",\n  SUM(delta_total_time) * 100.0 / NULLIF(t.total_runtime, 0) AS \"% of all runtime\"\nFROM filtered\nJOIN totals t ON true\nGROUP BY queryid, t.total_io, t.total_runtime\nORDER BY \"% of all runtime\" DESC\nLIMIT 100;\n",
